Output skills/agentic-engineering-github-tape-review/references/agentic-engineering-github-tape-review-output.gif

Require bash

Set Shell "bash"
Set Theme "GitHub Dark"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1440
Set Height 860
Set Padding 24
Set BorderRadius 18
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Framerate 12
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0
Set TypingSpeed 18ms

Hide
Type "cd ~/workspace/my-agent-skills"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "bash skills/agentic-engineering-github-tape-review/scripts/replay_terminal_output.sh"
Enter
Sleep 24s
